short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chrome extension developed for MultiVis Meeting.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Extension for collaborative interaction and Meeting control of Multivis Meeting. 

The tool provides full control of Multivis Meeting solution, allowing users to share desktops and applications, open Multivis apps, use the Multivis Pointer and join video conferences easily.
